{"tid":1782731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈正正是光復香港的重點","createTime":"2019-12-14T08:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T06:39:11.000Z","uid":50457,"like":118,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2575081940c8bee5e329fdb10a9d891901ad08d9","tid":1782731,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"未來幾年要係消費層面盡力去中國化，去藍絲化<br />\n<br />\n奶共, 中共，賣港的組織（包括NGO），商店，行業盡可能柸葛。<br />\n<br />\n大力推動廣東話教學，平價課程令新移民覺醒，令佢哋歸化香港<br />\n<br />\n從生活細節著手，面對中共寸步不讓。<br />\n<br />\n已經半年無食過吉野家，四個月無食過美心旗下任何一間快餐店，生活一樣過得好好。<br />\n<br />\n唔買淘寶，買Amazon, HKTV mall,光時，輕鬆無問題。<br />\n<br />\n對抗中共，就係從生活細節著手，總之每一間中資，藍資都唔可以係香港輕鬆賺錢"},{"pid":"b037858aff7f37be6a2e093e39059528beb51771","tid":1782731,"uid":34927,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要大家提供多啲黃店既選擇"},{"pid":"4c7ef668b6a1b01f7cd9cba6f3a9d7a14984cb13","tid":1782731,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b037858aff7f37be6a2e093e39059528beb51771","tid":1782731,"uid":34927,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要大家提供多啲黃店既選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"堅韓牛堅石燒時代冰淇室 <br />\n100%深黃"},{"pid":"61a7e5f35ecd3af7a9e10b2d7f2764492a5fae2e","tid":1782731,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228d218c25308897801881219180533dbccf9562","tid":1782731,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc319f346fcfc1df0dfe7cde9865a41d201bac44","tid":1782731,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:31:19.000Z","msg":"真，吉野家送都唔會食<br />\n同時間唔係對黃店太多規限<br />\n唔係一定要做乜做麥先叫黃店<br />\n保持獨立思考！"